"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"12月11日消息，彭博大宗商品高级策略师Mike McGlone认为，通货紧缩可能会在明年取代通货膨胀。大宗商品见顶和美国国债长期债券收益率下降表明，2022年通货紧缩力量有可能重振，这将对[比特币](https://www.bitcoin86.com/)和黄金产生积极影响。比特币将有望达到10万美元，而黄金交易价格将达到2000美元。（Cryptopotato）\",\"timestamp\":1639308965,\"title\":\"彭博分析师：通货紧缩将帮助比特币价格在2022年达到10万美元\"},\"digest\":\"GHSR7cP9I1rgK0ZgyLXI_Dd6DxzuF4O_VILqNQcv4dE\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x4948d33A02B9a0e0B8B8B53dc5cbF5D7C396Ae72\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"N4kHHEnQ9O9jZ9gYPAM_aCAsgrEwRCFe_ZjjfLDKw9o\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"8Ny-0bpRdJJ_NPcZUIJcb__9KvAlwX1z3BwlQ404m18\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"pQ1O_mG5IO7u2mg_6OFqMhzIW_jdPKasw0FPswLpgoHFZaneaX2A8EXtC-QWzGMtbpA4qmeq3iAGZgzQk67Hww\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x9683d13a5ab028da6c0070f0f2d0b6fac086f528a742d9f71afc2a8296eee1033fea1d85b1318738a858cb92fc65f7af31b68e8c6b875a4df846fc6cfe389cc61b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"N4kHHEnQ9O9jZ9gYPAM_aCAsgrEwRCFe_ZjjfLDKw9o\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"8Ny-0bpRdJJ_NPcZUIJcb__9KvAlwX1z3BwlQ404m18\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"GHSR7cP9I1rgK0ZgyLXI_Dd6DxzuF4O_VILqNQcv4dE\"}"